{"tid":2222220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高銀金融停牌　涉內幕消息","createTime":"2020-09-29T03:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T07:03:01.000Z","uid":185631,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd9a596e1496864da4cd13e81c33800fe211a2be","tid":2222220,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"高銀金融(00530)股份停牌，以待刊發有關其內幕消息之公告，該股停牌前報1.01港元。<br />\n<br />\n地產顧問服務公司萊坊周一(28日)表示，獲委託為獨家代理，放售高銀金融旗下，位於九龍灣啟祥道17號的高銀金融國際中心，遞交意向書截止日期為2020年11月11日正午12時正。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，是次物業放售是由債權人所委託的接管人及經理人提出，高銀金融並未公開表態是否同意放售該物業，亦未知會否有跟進行動。"},{"pid":"2218a07fd11f1f9d30262e5354915d03d8a6f2b9","tid":2222220,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"boom"},{"pid":"70f047a9eab386a4877f8d34c36c147e9ebfe507","tid":2222220,"uid":9116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"物業又淪為銀主盤，而家又內幕交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33f54f55fc66dbe51bbfe8cfea8c6a8128573a0","tid":2222220,"uid":299694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"10月都未到就又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aff0a3af6680d2cc631ddaeb3d7a2240d14fea","tid":2222220,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"被放盤？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc43061a99a4a3f124543fd3c8d7d7a239519cdd","tid":2222220,"uid":27072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"好心就快d執柒左佢，日日搵水魚做白武士，轉頭又放人飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f14601da4a3fa872e50f185e5ea9a8e7a546d07","tid":2222220,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi